Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:03:03.43,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}本格的な鬱の日差しが肌をこぼしていくように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:03:03.43,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}正如炎炎烈日傾灑在肌膚上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:12.40,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}私もあなたに恋に焦がれる　海へドライブ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:12.40,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}我也在去海邊兜風的時候對你一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.98,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}運転する横顔慣れる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.98,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}習慣了你開車時的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.78,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}潮風が気持ちいい Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.78,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}夏日的海風 清爽心怡的 Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.91,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.91,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.45,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}ビッチバレーするカラフルなウェア
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.45,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}沙灘排球時五顏六色的裝束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.16,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}砂浜に咲く花みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.16,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}就像在沙灘上綻開的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.42,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.42,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.84,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}あなたの心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.84,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}其實我真的好想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:40.17,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}もっと　もっと　近くに感じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:40.17,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}更近 更近的感受你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.97,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}私だけ見て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.97,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}請只注視著我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.35,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.35,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:56.86,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}服と膨らんだ胸の思い唇に乗せて伝えたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:56.86,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}好想將那滿脹的思念之情用雙唇傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.61,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.61,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.24,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.24,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.49,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}だからさ　kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.49,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}所以呀 我要 Kiss you
